#

Spicy Mango Glazed Chicken Thighs

$15.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

QuickPopularSavorySweet and Spicy

Description

Juicy chicken thighs coated in a sweet and spicy mango glaze, perfect for a quick and delicious dinner.

Ingredients

  • Chicken thighs: 4 pieces
  • Mango puree: 1/2 cup
  • Honey: 2 tablespoons
  • Soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Ginger: 1 tablespoon, grated
  • Red pepper flakes: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Green onions: 2, chopped for garnish
